Threat Title:Potential Data Repudiation by Vehicle Restricted Lanes Application;Threat Category:Repudiation;Description:Vehicle Restricted Lanes Application claims that it did not receive data from a source outside the trust boundary. Consider using logging or auditing to record the source, time, and summary of the received data.;
